"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-08-05-paris-2024-olympics-ofili-reflects-on-womens-200m-semi-final-feat\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published  on  By  Favour Ofili has reflected on her impressive performance in the women's 200m at the ongoing 2024 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 130, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ofili won her heat in blistering fashion, coasting home in a time of 22.24s.\", \"from\": 132, \"to\": 208, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 21-year-old could not compete in the women's 100m after she was not registered by officials of the Athletics Federation of Nigeria (AFN) and Nigeria Olympic Committee (NOC).\", \"from\": 210, \"to\": 387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 346, \"end\": 349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Assembly_of_First_Nations\", \"score\": 0.819267767028785, \"rank\": 0.22059943622247014, \"text\": \"AFN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Assembly_of_First_Nations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Assembly_of_First_Nations\"}, {\"begin\": 355, \"end\": 380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nigeria Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 382, \"end\": 385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9973560831366953, \"rank\": 0.002650925681864348, \"text\": \"NOC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Delta-State-born athlete said she was determined to showcase her talents at the games.\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 479, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Despite the setbacks, I was determined to shine.\", \"from\": 481, \"to\": 530, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mental preparation was key.\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 558, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Regardless of what happened, I was determined to be ready,\\\" Ofili was quoted by making of champions.\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 659, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I step on the track, I aim to cross the line before anyone else.\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 731, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are all Olympians, and I treat every competitor the same,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 732, \"to\": 804, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Transfer: Stan Collymore warns Osimhen against Chelsea move  Ancelotti reveals when Mbappe will make his Real Madrid debut  Paris 2024 Olympics: Nigeria's dismal performance worries enthusiasts  Paris 2024 Olympics: D'Tigress' Wakama wins Best Coach award  Paris 2024 Olympics: Brume vows to  bounce back from disappointing outing  Paris 2024 Olympics: Sports Minister apologises to Nigerians after disastrous outing  Paris 2024 Olympics: Team Nigeria officially finishes without single medal  Paris 2024 Olympics: Nigeria's last medal hope Reuben crashes out in Wrestling  Copyright \\u00a9Daily Post Media Ltd\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 1411, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 816, \"end\": 830, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stan_Collymore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stan Collymore\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stan_Collymore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stan_Collymore\"}, {\"begin\": 853, \"end\": 860, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999629476413, \"rank\": 3.6973918930222235e-08, \"text\": \"Chelsea\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 867, \"end\": 876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/res